docs {
  Get all bot messages from a specific channel using the unified message system.
  
  **Endpoint:** GET /bots/messages/channel/{channelId}
  
  **Path Parameters:**
  - channelId (number): The ID of the channel
  
  **Response:**
  Returns only bot messages from the unified Message table (filtered by botChannelMemberId IS NOT NULL).
  
  ```json
  [
    {
      "id": 2,
